title: Werewolf the Apocalypse 20th Anniversary Collection Nov. Update
description:
Here is the November 2015th update to the Werewolf: The Apocalypse 20th Anniversary collection.

October's collection is here: https://thepiratebay.mn/torrent/12612631/Werewolf_the_Apocalypse_20th_Anniversary_Collection_(Oct._2015)

This month's update includes:

* SAS - Skinner
* Rites of Renown - When Will You Rage II (short stories)
* The Poison Tree (novel)

Thanks to user pcx64 on Demonoid for sharing them!
